{
  "dashboard": {
    "title": "Network Isolation & Security",
    "tags": ["slapenir", "security", "isolation"],
    "timezone": "browser",
    "schemaVersion": 16,
    "version": 1,
    "refresh": "10s",
    "panels": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "Network Isolation Status",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 0},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "agent_network_isolation_status",
            "legendFormat": "Isolation",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "reduceOptions": {"values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]},
          "graphMode": "none"
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "mappings": [
              {"value": 1, "text": "ENABLED", "color": "green"},
              {"value": 0, "text": "DISABLED", "color": "red"}
            ],
            "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "red"},
              {"value": 1, "color": "green"}
            ]},
            "unit": "none"
          }
        },
        "description": "Firewall traffic enforcement status"
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "title": "Internet Bypass Attempts Blocked",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 0},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "agent_bypass_attempts_total{type=\"internet\"}",
            "legendFormat": "Blocked",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "reduceOptions": {"values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]},
          "graphMode": "area"
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
              {"value": 1, "color": "red"}
            ]},
            "unit": "none"
          }
        },
        "description": "Direct internet access attempts blocked by firewall (should be 0)"
      },
      {
        "id": 3,
        "title": "DNS Bypass Attempts Blocked",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 0},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "agent_dns_bypass_attempts_total",
            "legendFormat": "Blocked",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "reduceOptions": {"values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]},
          "graphMode": "area"
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
              {"value": 1, "color": "red"}
            ]},
            "unit": "none"
          }
        },
        "description": "Direct DNS requests blocked (should be 0)"
      },
      {
        "id": 4,
        "title": "Allowed Destinations",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 0},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "agent_allowed_destinations",
            "legendFormat": "Rules",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "reduceOptions": {"values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]},
          "graphMode": "none"
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "yellow"}
            ]},
            "unit": "none"
          }
        },
        "description": "Number of firewall rules allowing outbound traffic"
      },
      {
        "id": 5,
        "title": "Traffic by Firewall Rule (packets)",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 6},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate(agent_traffic_enforce_packets[1m])",
            "legendFormat": "{{rule}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "pps"
          }
        },
        "description": "Packets per second processed by each firewall rule"
      },
      {
        "id": 6,
        "title": "Traffic Bytes by Rule",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 6},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate(agent_traffic_enforce_bytes[1m])",
            "legendFormat": "{{rule}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "Bps"
          }
        },
        "description": "Bytes per second processed by each firewall rule"
      },
      {
        "id": 7,
        "title": "Active Connections by State",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 14},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "agent_active_connections",
            "legendFormat": "{{state}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "description": "TCP connection states"
      },
      {
        "id": 8,
        "title": "Proxy Traffic (All Outbound)",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 14},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate(slapenir_proxy_http_requests_total[1m])",
            "legendFormat": "{{method}} {{status}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "description": "All outbound requests through proxy"
      },
      {
        "id": 9,
        "title": "Security Summary",
        "type": "table",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 22},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "agent_network_isolation_status",
            "legendFormat": "Network Isolation",
            "refId": "A",
            "format": "table",
            "instant": true
          },
          {
            "expr": "agent_bypass_attempts_total or vector(0)",
            "legendFormat": "Bypass Attempts",
            "refId": "B",
            "format": "table",
            "instant": true
          },
          {
            "expr": "agent_dns_bypass_attempts_total or vector(0)",
            "legendFormat": "DNS Bypass Attempts",
            "refId": "C",
            "format": "table",
            "instant": true
          },
          {
            "expr": "agent_allowed_destinations or vector(0)",
            "legendFormat": "Allowed Destinations",
            "refId": "D",
            "format": "table",
            "instant": true
          }
        ],
        "transformations": [
          {
            "id": "seriesToColumns",
            "options": {"byField": "Time"}
          }
        ],
        "description": "Security metrics summary"
      },
      {
        "id": 10,
        "title": "Default Drop Counter",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 30},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "agent_traffic_enforce_packets{rule=\"default_drop\"} or vector(0)",
            "legendFormat": "Dropped",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "reduceOptions": {"values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]},
          "graphMode": "area"
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
              {"value": 1, "color": "red"}
            ]},
            "unit": "none"
          }
        },
        "description": "Packets dropped by default firewall rule (should be 0)"
      },
      {
        "id": 11,
        "title": "Proxy Response Time",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 30},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, rate(slapenir_proxy_http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m]))",
            "legendFormat": "p95",
            "refId": "A"
          },
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, rate(slapenir_proxy_http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m]))",
            "legendFormat": "p50",
            "refId": "B"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "s"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 12,
        "title": "Traffic to Proxy (rule=proxy)",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 30},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "agent_traffic_enforce_packets{rule=\"proxy\"}",
            "legendFormat": "Packets",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "reduceOptions": {"values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]},
          "graphMode": "area"
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
              {"value": 0, "color": "green"}
            ]},
            "unit": "none"
          }
        },
        "description": "Packets sent through proxy (allowed)"
      },
      {
        "id": 13,
        "title": "Network Isolation Guarantee",
        "type": "text",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 36},
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "## Network Isolation Verification\n\nThis dashboard proves that:\n\n1. **All outbound traffic goes through the proxy** - The `proxy` rule shows traffic to 172.30.0.2:3000\n2. **No direct internet access** - The `default_drop` counter should be 0\n3. **No DNS bypass** - The `dns_block` counter should be 0\n4. **Firewall is active** - Network Isolation Status should be 1 (ENABLED)\n\n### What this means:\n- The agent CANNOT send requests directly to the internet\n- All HTTP/HTTPS requests must go through the proxy\n- The proxy sanitizes secrets before forwarding requests\n- No inbound connections from the internet are possible"
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
